%% Diagram: Streaming SSR with Suspense
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as SSR Server
    participant F as Fast data
    participant L as Slow data

    B->>S: GET /product/42
    S-->>B: shell + Suspense fallbacks (TTFB)
    Note over B: Renders shell\nFCP / LCP can fire
    par Resolve in parallel
        S->>F: query product
        F-->>S: 30 ms
        S-->>B: $RC swaps fallback A
    and
        S->>L: query recommendations
        L-->>S: 400 ms
        S-->>B: $RC swaps fallback B
    end
    S-->>B: close connection
    Note over B: Selective hydration\nper Suspense boundary
